    "refcode_short": "AH 5.2",
    "refcode_long": "The Adventist Home, p. 5.2 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<span class=\"non-egw-foreword\">Ellen G. White has written much and very valuable counsel for parents. She has touched upon every phase of the home, and offers specific instruction on many of the problems which give so much concern to thoughtful and often anxious parents today. Some years before her death, she indicated her desire to get out &ldquo;a book for Christian parents&rdquo; that would define &ldquo;the mother&apos;s duty and influence over her children.&rdquo; In the present work an endeavor has been made to fulfill this expectation.</span>",
    "puborder": 4,
    "translations": [
