    "refcode_short": "AH 5.3",
    "refcode_long": "The Adventist Home, p. 5.3 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<span class=\"non-egw-foreword\">This book, <em>The Adventist Home,</em> is at once a sort of handbook or manual for busy parents, and a pattern or ideal of what the home can and should become. Here are the answers to your many questions, the words of wisdom from the heavenly Father.</span>",
