    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<span class=\"non-egw-foreword\">This document has been prepared in the office of the Ellen G. White Publications. The work has been done in harmony with Mrs. White&apos;s instruction to her trustees in providing &ldquo;for the printing of compilations&rdquo; from her manuscripts, for they contain, she said, &ldquo;instruction that the Lord has given me for his people.&rdquo;</span>",
