    "refcode_short": "AH 6.2",
    "refcode_long": "The Adventist Home, p. 6.2 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<span class=\"non-egw-foreword\">Never in the history of the world has a book like this been needed more urgently than it is right now. Never have parents and children been more anxious for the right answer to the things which trouble them. Never have homes been in such jeopardy as they are today.</span>",
