    "refcode_long": "The Adventist Home, p. 6.3 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<span class=\"non-egw-foreword\">Every one of us knows that conditions in society are but a reflection of conditions in the homes of the nation. We likewise know that a change in the home will be mirrored in a changed society. To this end this Volume&mdash;<em>The Adventist Home</em>&mdash;has been prepared and, as a part of the Christian home library, is now sent forth on its important mission by the publishers and</span>",
